{"tid":1967399,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：直接予僱員程序繁複 增審批時間長 自僱MPF需活躍","createTime":"2020-04-11T01:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T08:52:26.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90de626a3ea115f01a3d1a243f3abab2fad517df","tid":1967399,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"羅致光︰直接資助僱員薪金程序較麻煩<br />\n11.04.2020 09:04<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局長羅致光在一個電台節目表示，補貼僱主五成工資的措施，如果改為直接資助僱員，處理程序較麻煩，透過僱主發放可減少爭拗，預計最快五月中接受申請，六月發放津貼，形容時間已是最短。羅致光說，如果再審視僱主減薪的幅度是否合理，需翻查貿易紀錄，工作量可能增100倍。羅致光指，首輪防疫抗疫基金構思時，未有預期歐美地區的疫情惡化，現時全球經濟進入衰退，亦不知何時完結，向僱主補貼六個月薪金資助是合理。<br />\n<br />\n至於計劃向有強積金供款的自僱人士派發一筆過7500元，羅致光指，計劃參考去年的強積金供款紀錄，如果戶口仍活躍，就會派發津貼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280102&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280102%26csid%3D261_341&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479Vaof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=cf32a6d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280102&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"190df039f72c478f1e9f377dce7f2a0d8d41b5dd","tid":1967399,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"返新工未夠一個月有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a41e72e3a04dcef2467a7f4aa21a50769d16335","tid":1967399,"uid":27670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"選舉近了 梗係俾僱主<br />\n員工wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79d9cf8c8ba7b5a20dccbdbf1df2a2e73bc1bcf","tid":1967399,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"係要有供款定有run緊？"},{"pid":"14a72c66fac3354454d60c30144de71b9e5e512e","tid":1967399,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"